The end goal workflow of the gem:
- "lazy-translate [source path] [config_path]


1.
  %p Some text
2.
  %p
    Some long long
    long long text
3.
  %p
    Some long
    %strong text
    with
    %em some html
4.
  %p
    Some text
    = some_var
    with variables
5.
  %p
    = link_to('Text inside link', path)
    = image_tag 'Text inside any call', img
6.
  %p
    img{alt: 'Text inside attributes'}
